{"tid":2054306,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港公務員必須「貫徹新時代中國共產黨的組織路線」","createTime":"2020-06-07T05:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:15:13.000Z","uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a92b8f1095faa987bbf45f953a3428654453447c","tid":2054306,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"聶德權話香港公務員係中國公務員。咁「中國公務員」要點樣？其實中國係有《中國公務員法》，其中第四條：<br />\n<br />\n「公務員制度堅持中國共產黨領導，堅持以馬克思列寧主義、毛澤東思想、鄧小平理論、「三個代表」重要思想、科學發展觀、習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想為指導，貫徹社會主義初級階段的基本路線，貫徹新時代中國共產黨的組織路線，堅持黨管幹部原則。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，按第53條規定，公務員不得打麻雀、玩骰中、鋤大D，以及進行算命、睇風水、睇星座預測等迷信活動：<br />\n<br />\n「公務員必須遵守紀律，不得有下列行為：參與或者支持色情、吸毒、<span style=\"color: orange;\">賭博、迷信</span>等活動。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530660-20200607.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530660-20200607.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUu8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=f7a8a7e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530660-20200607.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4a89e21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530660-20200607.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/BIG5/n1/2019/0402/c64387-31008811.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn1%2F2019%2F0402%2Fc64387-31008811.html&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUu8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=8e2bc5c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/BIG5/n1/2019/0402/c64387-31008811.html</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0iBFBs1MH3I&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUu8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=9147f624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0iBFBs1MH3I</a>"},{"pid":"fe